</div>

## Artifact Type (22)

Set \`artifact_type\` in \`task.toml\` to an array of the labels that best describe the central artifacts. Multiple labels are allowed. Use the exact lowercase \`snake_case\` form as listed in **\`.dynamo/diversity-taxonomy.toml\`** (the source of truth).

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-4">
  <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-muted text-foreground px-3 py-1 text-sm font-mono">codebase</span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-muted text-foreground px-3 py-1 text-sm font-mono">single_script_or_program</span>
